ttps://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"=
image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1313874132" data-linked-res=
ource-container-version=3D"12" alt=3D"" width=3D"468"></span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(28,30,33);">As per PACT recommendation, Step =
3 - Contract Sharing can happen via open version PACT Broker or using comme=
rcial tool such as Pactflow</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(28,30,33);">In order to avoid the maintenance=
 overhead, MESH customised the Step 3 via existing centralised artifactory =
and with set of python based pipeline helpers. </span></li>
</ul>
<h1 id=3D"APIContractTestingGuidelines-HowContractTestingworksinMesh"><span=
 style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>How Contract Testing works in Mesh<=
/strong></span></h1>
