style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>What is API Contract (PACT) Test:</s=
trong></span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"APIContractTestingGuidelines-Consumer'sContractTest:"><strong><sp=
an style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);">Consumer's Contract Test:</span></strong>=
</h2>
<p><br></p>
