<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">As part of this pipeline run:</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">decrypts the encrypted data file (if=
 exist)</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">fetches the api key, secret from axw=
ay for the component name being passed in</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">triggers the newman runner for the i=
ntegration_tests_postman_collection.json passing the environment file (prep=
ared based on the above fetched api key, secret) and the data file (if exis=
t) as arguments</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">generates the junit and newman html =
report</span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Note to Platform Support team</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">if the secret 'a' for decryption is =
compromised, pass the ENVSEC_ACTIVE_KEY 'b' during custom Rum =E2=80=93 to =
make use of the backup secret key.</span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
