<h1 id=3D"APIVirtualizationinMesh-MeshBuiltInSolutionwithMockoon:"><span st=
yle=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>Mesh Built In Solution with Mockoon:</=
strong></span></h1>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);">To understand how the solution is d=
esigned within Mesh Platform - refer here: </span><span style=3D"color: rgb=
(0,0,128);"><strong><a href=3D"/display/MD/Service+Virtualization">Service =
Virtualization</a></strong></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Always make sure to create mocks in local, test in local first before tr=
ying to get deployed into non prod environments.</p>
<h1 id=3D"APIVirtualizationinMesh-IntegratewithMockoonforlocalAPItesting:">=
<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>Integrate with Mockoon for loc=
al API testing:</strong></span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"APIVirtualizationinMesh-SCENARIO:.1"><strong><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(0,0,128);">SCENARIO:</span></strong></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>GIVEN</strong> <span style=
=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">I am the API or MFE owner (developer or tester) =
of "X" </span></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>AND</strong> <span style=3D=
"color: rgb(0,51,102);">"X" is dependent on other api "Y"</span></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>WHEN</strong>&nbsp;</span><=
span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">M=
ockoon server (GUI or CLI) runs in localhost:3010 having mocked "Y" endpoin=
ts</span></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102)=
;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>AND</strong></span> <span s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">I have =
the local instance of "X" running in my laptop <em>via</em> <strong>mesh ru=
n -m True</strong></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>THEN</strong><span style=3D=
"color: rgb(0,51,102);"> I can test&nbsp; "X" in localhost:8080 which is po=
inted to "Y" in localhost:3010</span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<h3 id=3D"APIVirtualizationinMesh-StartMockoonin3010Port"><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(0,0,128);"><strong>Start Mockoon in 3010 Port</strong></span></h3>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102)=
;">Once the endpoints are mocked</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102=
);">Enable the proxy redirection to gateway url (dev1 or sit1 environment) =
whichever environment it need to be redirected</span></span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102=
);">start the server in 3010 port</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102)=
;">Proxy redirection can be configured under Proxy in Mockoon GUI as below.=
</span></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102)=
;">Note:&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102)=
;"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" width=
=3D"468" src=3D"257dfcf3f88a7c0b2d08629e984f58e54d870f85a74872342d07328ef97=
b8de4" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/1557945143/image-2023-12-4_1=
6-45-25.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1701668725553&amp;api=3Dv2" =
data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1557949887" =
data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment"=
 data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-2023-12-4_16-45-25.png" data-b=
ase-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-cont=
ent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1557945143" dat=
a-linked-resource-container-version=3D"39" alt=3D"" height=3D"125"></span><=
/span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102)=
;">Port can be configured under Settings in Mockoon GUI as below</span></sp=
an></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,128);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102)=
;"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" width=
